{"word":"G5409 - φορέω - phoréō - for-eh'-o - Bear","slug":"G5409","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">φορέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>phoréō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>for-eh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Bear"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"- Original: <b><el>φορέω</el></b> <p />- Transliteration: <b>Phoreo</b> <p />- Phonetic: <b>for-eh'-o</b> <p class=\"def\">- Definition: </p> <p class='li260'><b>1.</b> to bear constantly, wear </p> <p class='li520'><b>a.</b> of clothing, garments, armour </p> <p class=\"origin\"/>- Origin: from <a href=\"#/G5411\">G5411</a> <p />- TDNT entry: 10:23,1 <p />- Part(s) of speech: Verb <p />- Strong's: From <a href=\"#/G5411\">G5411</a>; to <i>have a burden</i> that is (by analogy) to <i>wear</i> as clothing or a constant <b>accompaniment</b>: - bear wear. "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1308\">G1308</a>, <a href=\"#/G1313\">G1313</a>, <a href=\"#/G2018\">G2018</a>, <a href=\"#/G399\">G399</a>, <a href=\"#/G4374\">G4374</a>, <a href=\"#/G4376\">G4376</a>, <a href=\"#/G4851\">G4851</a>, <a href=\"#/G5342\">G5342</a>, <a href=\"#/G5411\">G5411</a>, <a href=\"#/G5412\">G5412</a>, <a href=\"#/G5413\">G5413</a>, <a href=\"#/G5414\">G5414</a>"}]}